reviewText: I would have rather had received a posture workout at 1/2 hour length than just instruction of each exercise to do which in length was only 13 minutes.  This is retailed overpriced, not the vendors fault but the manufacturer.  I am not bothering to return but this is not a favorite.
Simple, easy-to-follow exercises and stretches. And it comes with the little resistance loop, so it gave me everything I needed to start right away.
